Jimmy: 26 year old tattooed streetsmart scrapper weighing in at 184 pounds. Ivan: 27 year old exotic looking stud weighing in at 172. Both nude. (3) TONY VALOR VS MARK MARIANO. Tony: 1st match for this 5'6" 21 year old 180 pound musclegod. Mark: Handsome 21 year old swimmer weighing in at 170 pounds. Muscleboy Tony is a Can-Am star-on-the-rise with 3 matches in this brochure guaranteed to light your fire.
title: Toronto Amateur Pro Wrestling
